### TMDB Movie Video API Testing
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or copy to Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login First (Get Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-email@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### 2. Add TMDB Movie Video URL (Sample - Big Buck Bunny)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tmdb-movie/video
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tmdbId": 278,
  "title": "The Shawshank Redemption (Test)",
  "videoUrl": "https://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/gtv-videos-bucket/sample/BigBuckBunny.mp4",
  "source": "external"
}

### 3. Add Another Movie (Elephant Dream)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tmdb-movie/video
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tmdbId": 550,
  "title": "Fight Club (Test)",
  "videoUrl": "https://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/gtv-videos-bucket/sample/ElephantsDream.mp4",
  "source": "external"
}

### 4. Get All TMDB Movies with Videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tmdb-movies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Specific TMDB Movie Details (Check if hasFullMovie is true)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/tmdb/278
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Delete TMDB Movie Video (Replace MONGODB_ID with actual _id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tmdb-movie/MONGODB_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
